               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18460330-name-449" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18460330-name-449" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460330-name-449" type="surname" value="LAMONT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460330-name-449" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES LAMONT</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a commander in the Royal Navy. On the after<lb></lb>noon of the 28th of March I was in St. Paul's Church-yard—a gentleman spoke to me, and I looked for my handkerchief, which had been in my coat pocket—I found it was gone—I saw the prisoner in custody, and saw it taken from his breast—this is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Is it not possible you might have dropped it? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> It is possible, certainly—I did not feel you at my pocket.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18460330-name-450" type="witnessName">
