                        <interp inst="t18460330-name-450" type="given" value="FREDERICK WILLIAM"></interp>FREDERICK WILLIAM LAWRENCE</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at No. 18, White Conduit-grove. I was passing the captain and another gentleman, who were walking arm-in-arm in St. Paul's Church-yard—I saw the prisoner take this handkerchief from the captain's pocket and put it into his breast—I followed him across Cheapside and took him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I picked up the gentleman's handkerchief; I saw it lying upon the ground. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> I was close to him—I am sure he did not pick it up—it was his taking it out of the pocket attracted my attention.</p>
